'''Galdor''' can refer to:
*[[Galdor (elf of Gondolin)]], the lord of the [[House of the Tree]].
*[[Galdor (Lord of Dor-lómin)]], father of [[Húrin|Húrin Thalion]] who died before the [[Nirnaeth Arnoediad]].
*[[Galdor (elf of the Havens)]], [[Círdan]]'s representative at the [[Council of Elrond]].
*[[Galdor (man of Rohan)]], seneschal of [[Edoras]].
